Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive

Class SynchronizedDoubleBooleanMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive.SynchronizedDoubleBooleanMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, BooleanIterable, BooleanValuesMap, DoubleBooleanMap, MutableBooleanValuesMap, MutableDoubleBooleanMap, PrimitiveIterable

    public class SynchronizedDoubleBooleanMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableDoubleBooleanMap, java.io.Serializable
    A synchronized view of a MutableDoubleBooleanMap. It is imperative that the user manually synchronize on the collection when iterating over it using the MutableBooleanIterator as per Collections.synchronizedCollection(Collection).

    This file was automatically generated from template file synchronizedPrimitivePrimitiveMap.stg.

    Since:
    3.1.
